profile:
Thank you to all of my wonderful clients for making me the 'best of' for the second year in a row! 

Stan Bernard Carpentry is a complete residential carpentry service offering construction of decks, interlocking and pavement, installation of tiles, trim work, additions and restorations from start to finish. We are a family owned business in operation for over 20 years. We also provide commercial building maintenance and general upkeep.
service_area: We provide a variety of building services to Brockville, Prescott, Spencerville, Cardinal, Iroquois, Kemptville and the surrounding areas.
